    "Search actions for \"Add Wallet Transaction to YNAB\" (YNAB, optionally split with Splitwise) or \"Add Wallet Transaction to Splitwise\" (Splitwise only). Tap \"Amount\", scroll right, then select \"Shortcut Input\"." : {
      "localizations" : {
